# 6ixSeven Gold

Dark themed Next.js website for your investment dashboard.

## Run locally
```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

## Deploy
This project is ready for a fresh GitHub repository and can be deployed to Vercel as a Next.js app.

## Files
- app/layout.tsx
- app/page.tsx
- app/globals.css
- package.json
- next.config.mjs
- tsconfig.json
- next-env.d.ts
